3i Group May Create a Fund with China Government, Cinco Says

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-02-28T07:21:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/3i-group-may-create-a-fund-with-china-government-cinco-says.html
  3i Group Plc  is negotiating with
China’s government for the creation of a fund, Cinco Dias said,
citing Chief Executive Officer Michael Queen.  The fund may be ready this year although the size hasn’t
been set, the newspaper said, citing Queen.  The private equity firm also plans to set up in two or
three years a 5 billion euro ($7 billion) fund which will invest
in  Europe , Queen told Cinco Dias.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
 eduarterubia@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Armstrong at 
 Parmstrong10@bloomberg.net  